35 安培，電阻值為 5.657×10-5Ω，熱抗阻為 378），試計算在常溫 25℃下須通多大
電流值，其絕緣物溫度將超過最高容許溫度值。（25分）', '[]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:18+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "ef1a76cce130", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "103060", "c": "401", "s": "0701", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "甲、申論題部分", "subject": "火災學", "year": "103", "exam_name": "103年專門驗船師、第一次食品技師考試消防設備人員地政士專責報關人員保險員考試", "original_question_number": "三", "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "fire-equipment-engineer", "db_exam_id": "fire-eq-eng"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('fire-eq-eng-moex-00819', 'fire-eq-eng', 'fire-eq-eng-moex-103-39ca095a', 'sub-fire-eq-eng-05', NULL, 'essay', '試述何謂建築物正煙囪效應及逆煙囪效應？茲有某棟 16 層飯店大樓，其第 13 樓及
